 {r}←Shutdown INI;parms;event
⍝ INI can be either ⍬ or the instance of the Plodder INI file, If it is the QuitEvent is send to the root
 r←⍬
 WindowsEventLog'Shutting down'
 {6::shy←⍬ ⋄ 1:shy←##.DRC.Close'.'}⍬
 ##.⎕EX'DRC'
 :If ~(⊂INI)∊''⍬
 :AndIf 9=⎕NC'INI'
     :Trap 0
         event←INI.Get'EVENTS:QuitEvent'
         r←⎕NQ'.'event
     :EndTrap
 :EndIf
 {}⎕TKILL ⎕TNUMS~⎕TID    ⍝ Kill everything but zero and itself
 :If A.IsDevelopment
     ⎕←'***'
     →
 :Else
     ⎕OFF
 :EndIf
 ⍝Done
